X11-GUITest-record version 0.15
===============================

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  - X11::GUITest (optional)
  - Xlib-devel

To use this module please activate the record extension in the config of the X-Server:

  - under selection "Module"
     Load           "record"

If you want to test this module please activate the record extension first and then try "make test". Otherwise
the test will be disabled.

  
